flowRoot.flowPara: Travel time and Δv are averaged over 10 sample years in 23 year intervals. Plock has a range of values because of its elliptical orbit. Travel times are only rough estimates. Due to the great distances involved, a minor difference in phase angle can have a large effect. Values calculated by Rosco P. Coltrane using TriggerAu's Transfer Window Planner Mod.
Based on Misucat's Map for OPM 1.7.5 from May 5th 2015
